These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, emerald, ivory
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, havana, tiparillo
1. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere between the person who likes orange and the havana-smoker##7
2. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
3. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Color   | ivory | emerald | orange |
| Cigar           | havana  | tiparillo     | ritmeester  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
City: miami, nizza, rome
3 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog, rabbit
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person traveling to rome and the owner of the hedgehog##7
3. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| City   | nizza | miami | rome |
| Pet     | hedgehog       | rabbit     | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, white, ebony
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, march, may
1. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who's birthday is in september##7
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Color    | fuchsia | white | ebony  |
| Birthday   | may  | march  | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
House: art-deco, craftsman, futuristic
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, mirinda
1. the art-deco house is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the craftsman house##7
2. the person drinking cola is not the art-deco house##6
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| House           | craftsman | art-deco | futuristic     |
| Beverage   | cola    | milk          | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, june, december
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, aristoff, montecristo
1. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere between the montecristo-smoker and the person who's birthday is in june##7
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Birthday   | october      | december     | june   |
| Cigar     | montecristo | aristoff | bolivar |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, photography, hiking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, dahlia
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
2. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the person who growsdahlia and the person who's hobby is gardening##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | hiking    | photography     | gardening     |
| Flower   | dahlia | sunflower | poppy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
City: new-york, miami, edinburgh
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person traveling to new-york and the person driving the skateboard##7
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| City     | edinburgh       | miami      | new-york       |
| Transport   | skateboard | ship | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, van, motorbike
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
2. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person driving the van##7
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Transport           | motorbike | trike  | van |
| Game   | backgammon      | mah-jongg | domino      |

