.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, reading
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, january, september
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's birthday is in january##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles   | reading    | magic-tricks |
| Birthday      | september | october | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, canasta
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, swimming
1. the person playing chess is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is badminton##7
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is not the person playing canasta##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Game         | canasta | chess | snooker |
| Sport   | sailing    | swimming    | badminton         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
House: tower, farmhouse, craftsman
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, almond-milk
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the tower house##7
3. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| House          | tower  | craftsman       | farmhouse     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice | sprite |

