.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-13::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, ship
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, december, august
1. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in august##7
2. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person driving the car##7
4. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Transport      | quad-bike     | ship | car |
| Birthday   | september | december    | august |

