.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-14::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, musical
3 different games are played: bridge, canasta, whist
1. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
2. the person playing whist is the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing whist and the person watching adventure movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre        | horror | musical | adventure |
| Game   | whist  | canasta       | bridge      |

