.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, black, brown
City: liverpool, nizza, hannover
1. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5
2. the person who likes brown is the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who likes black is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to liverpool##7
4. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Color          | brown | black     | blue   |
| City   | hannover   | nizza | liverpool |

