.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-18::.
3 different games are played: bridge, billiard, monopoly
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, farmhouse
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing monopoly is the gothic-revival house##1
3. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the ranch-style house and the person playing bridge##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Game   | billiard     | monopoly | bridge |
| House     | ranch-style | gothic-revival | farmhouse |

