.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
City: marseilles, edinburgh, hannover
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, sudoku, puzzles
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
3. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| City   | edinburgh      | hannover     | marseilles |
| Hobby        | puzzles | rock-climbing | sudoku    |

 